title: The Cowboys' QB Situation
description:
Laura Rutledge and the NFL Live Crew discuss the Cowboy’s QB situation following Cooper Rush’s performance, Mac Jones likely missing multiple games with a high ankle sprain and the Dolphins’ and Bengals’ comments leading into their game this Thursday night.
